works.description:
The text on our homepage as detailed below:

Here at Voodoo DesignWorks, we’re not just a sign company. We stand out  
from the competition and we’ll make you stand out too.

Our ‘top down’ design services cover every aspect of your image-making  
requirements from sign and graphic design through to production and  
installation. Our services include corporate fleet vehicle livery, one-off  
vehicle graphics, outdoor durable large format printing, point of sale  
signage, window graphics, banners, exhibition displays and much, much more.

Our skilled, in-house sign makers and fabricators are capable of turning  
these imaginative design ideas into a reality that will really make your  
image sparkle.

If you're looking for something more from your sign maker, whether you want  
us to work our magic from scratch, or simply require reproductions of  
existing jobs, click on the links below to see how Voodoo Design can work  
for you.
